title: J.D. Vance Elected Senator in Ohio
description: J.D. Vance, the Republican author of “Hillbilly Elegy,” defeated Representative Tim Ryan. Mr. Vance was once a sharp critic of Donald J. Trump but refashioned himself.
dc:creator: Katie Glueck
media:credit: Maddie McGarvey for The New York Times
media:description: J.D. Vance at a town-hall-style event that Fox News hosted in Columbus, Ohio, last week.
